rong>Tools: </strong>Procreate dreams</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"60%\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.2\"}},\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-x-large-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.2\">Animated dunk</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fill\",\"flexSize\":null}}} -->\n<p>Floating through the skies, <em>papa jump </em>defying physics. Following through Numencaniq\'s <a href=\"https://www.domestika.org/en/courses/235-animacion-2d-con-photoshop-dibujo-camara-y-accion\">2D camera course</a>, which is focused on framing and camera movements, I went through an experimentation path with Procreate Dreams. Organizing and planning a complex scene required an intense use of anatomy and imagination.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By planning the dunk and cameras beforehand I was able to think on spacing, timing and extreme limb movements. Being able to have a mental map of what a flat movement could be allowed me to go quick and not overthink each of the positions, focusing on the impressions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"},\"blockGap\":\"0\",\"margin\":{\